%% Source for assets/diagrams/saga-state-machine.svg
%% Saga state machine: happy path with event-driven transitions, a compensation
%% branch, and a checkpoint store (KV / Prisma) persisting state on each transition.
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending
    Pending --> Reserving: reserve
    Reserving --> Charging: charge
    Charging --> Shipping: ship
    Shipping --> Completed: done
    Completed --> [*]

    Charging --> Refunding: fail
    Refunding --> Failed: compensate
    Failed --> [*]

    note right of Shipping
        Each transition persists state to the
        checkpoint store (KV / Prisma).
    end note
